room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: We had The Cellar and got super scared and it was great. It was an office retreat and we had a lot of fun. Would go again in a heartbeat.

room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: We had a group of 6 for "The Cellar". Richard ran out room and was so much fun! We had an awesome time and will be back to do more rooms! I highly recommend trying out whatever themed room. Request Richard because he's great at explaining and running a room!

room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: This was the best experience ever! I would highly recommend it to anyone who is thinking about trying it.

room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: So fun! I would recommend to everyone and will! It was tough but not to the point u have no way to get out. Can't wait to go back and defeat another room:)

room_title: Escape room "The Cellar" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
review: We had such an amazing experience in The Cellar. I would highly recommend this to everyone. Bailey was AMAZING! Thanks Escape Chamber and Bailey for making this such a fun and exciting experience!!!
